export const config = {
  env: process.env.REACT_APP_ENV,
  apiUrl: process.env.REACT_APP_API_URL,
  derivativeApi: process.env.REACT_APP_DERIVATIVE_API_URL,
  deferredApi: process.env.REACT_APP_DEFERRED_API_URL,
  fundingApi: process.env.REACT_APP_FUNDING_API_URL,
  soldApi: process.env.REACT_APP_SOLD_API_URL,
  uploadCSVApi: process.env.REACT_APP_UPLOAD_CSV_API_URL,
  uploadLeadsCSVApi: process.env.REACT_APP_LEADS_UPLOAD_CSV_API_URL,
  templateApi: process.env.REACT_APP_TEMPLATE_API_URL,
  publicStripe: process.env.REACT_APP_PUBLIC_KEY_STRIPE,
  vapiKey: process.env.REACT_APP_VAPI_KEY,
  thomasAssistant: process.env.REACT_APP_THOMAS_ASSISTANT,
  hemaAssistant: process.env.REACT_APP_HEMMA_ASSISTANT,
  alejandraAssistant: process.env.REACT_APP_ALEJANDRA_ASSISTANT,
  jessiAssistant: process.env.REACT_APP_JESSI_ASSISTANT,
  miraAssistant: process.env.REACT_APP_MIRA_ASSISTANT,
  squadAssistant: process.env.REACT_APP_SQUAD_ASSISTANT,
}

export const walletConfig = {
  platformId: 'ab88f574-5e68-45c2-907a-623414b3b7b1',
}
